{"lemma":"شَهْوَةٌ","slug":"شَهْوَةٌ","root":"ش.ه.#","root_slug":"ش-ه-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ه-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَهْوَة","root":"شهو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23245"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lust; craving; greed; yearning; passion"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃah.wa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23245","headword_ar":"شَهْوَةٌ","root":"$hw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned above as an inf. n.] is a word of well-known meaning; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yearning, of the soul for a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, Msb, TA;) [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a thing gratifying to sense:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense, desire;"},{"kind":"text","text":"particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it has a more intensive signification than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iraAdapN","text_ar":"اـِرَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"the intelligent agree in opinion that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is not commendable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"frs","text_ar":"فرس"},{"kind":"text","text":":) [being either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lawful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unlawful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it may be rendered as above: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appetite:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appetence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carnal lust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the present state of existence, it is of two sorts,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAdiqapN","text_ar":"صَادِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"true"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaA*ibapN","text_ar":"كَاذِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"false"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; the former being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that without which the body becomes in an unsound state, as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahowap","text_ar":"شَهْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for food on the occasion of hunger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the latter being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that without which the body does not become in an unsound state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes it is applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object of desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing desired"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (Er-Rághib, TA:) and agreeably with this last explanation the first of the following pls. is used in the Kur iii. 12: (Ksh, Bd, Jel:) sometimes also it is applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faculty to which a thing is made an object of desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (Er-Rághib, TA:) [also, to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gratification of venereal lust;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus in the K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$fr","text_ar":"شفر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afirato","text_ar":"شَفِرَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afirapN","text_ar":"شَفِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahawaAtN","text_ar":"شَهَوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ohiyapN","text_ar":"اَشْهِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uhFY","text_ar":"شُهًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the last mentioned by AHei, and a rare instance of a pl. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEalN","text_ar":"فُعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from a sing. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolapN","text_ar":"فَعْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"having an infirm letter for its last radical, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhFY","text_ar":"جُهًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahowapN","text_ar":"جَهْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qurFY","text_ar":"قُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroyapN","text_ar":"قَرْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ahowataAni","text_ar":"الشَّهْوَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two appetites, that of the stomach and that of the generative organ."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ahowapu Alxafiy~apu","text_ar":"الشَّهْوَةُ الخَفِيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The latent desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] mentioned in a trad. is said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any act of disobedience which one conceives in his mind, and upon which he resolves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one's seeing a beautiful young woman, and lowering his eyes, then looking with his heart, and imaging her to his mind, and so tempting himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahowapu AlT~iyni","text_ar":"شَهْوَةُ الطِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The longing for clay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is app. used as a general term for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"malacia:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~aADN","text_ar":"حُمَّاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Ksh","Bd","Jel","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}